thread.title: Nickola Lane
thread.title_full: Tony Kealys reviewed by Nickola Lane

author: Nickola Lane
title: Nickola Lane
text: Ordered a little nipper on line at the start of January got a fantastic offer on it and it's the best buggy I've ever had so light and easy to push and plenty of room and comfy for my 16 month old, the buggy was delivered for free within a matter of days absolutely brilliant service from start to finish I have recommended tony Kealys to lots of friends and will never shop anywhere else from now on
